reviewText: Ugly George WAS an original -- but he's also a bore and a drag, as this film painfully documents.  Pass.

This is a documentary i wish there were more footage of the women being shown getting naked & less interviews. Some of the N.Y. background history was interesting. If your looking for a lot of women getting naked you will be very unhappy at the small amount footage that is really in it but for a low Amazon price its worth a look the main deptartment stores won't carry this so mail order is the main option.
